main event: A UFO sighting was reported over St. Paul, Minnesota on 19 September 1955.
interesting points: The object was described as a tear drop shape with a white light in the center., The observation lasted for 10 minutes., Initial conclusions suggested the object could be a balloon, aircraft, or astronomical phenomenon., There were children in the yard who witnessed the sighting., The object disappeared into haze after the observation.
sighted object: tear drop shaped object with a white light in the center
